physical design
--------------------
separate two-way traffic on thru-ways and boulevards

phased materials
    gravel
    asphalt
    stone

phased buildout
    rural: gravel forever
    thru-way: starts as two lane rd with basic bike/ped facilties, eventually bus facilties and high quality bike/ped accommodations

user separation on thru-ways and boulevards

alleys/driveways
    driveways in rural, everything else should be alley access--no driveways allowed

master street plan governs locations of streets
    deviations only allowed through public process, must conform to
    standards for connectivity




maintenance
-----------------------
snow removal
weed control/mowing
